<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Withdrawal Rejection - WealthWise</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.9rem;
    }
    .content h3 {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
      color: #125699;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #444;
    }
    .highlight {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-left: 4px solid #1e90ff;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #333;
    }
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: #1e90ff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #125699;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #777;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #1e90ff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>WealthWise</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h3>Hello {{name}},</h3>
      <p>
        We regret to inform you that your withdrawal request of 
        <strong>${{amount}}</strong> could not be processed at this time.
      </p>
      <div class="highlight">
        <p><strong>Wallet Address:</strong> {{walletAddress}}</p>
      </div>
      <p>
        Please ensure all details provided are accurate. If you believe this was a mistake or need further clarification, our support team is here to help you.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-container">
        <a href="https://www.wealthwise.com/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for trusting <strong>WealthWise</strong>.</p>
      <p>Visit our website: <a href="https://www.wealthwise.com">www.wealthwise.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
